snippet.title: Introducing Nightmare Lyre To Fret Smasher
snippet.description:
Fret Smasher is a brand new band styled rhythm game that is aimed to not only bring back classic play, but also new ways of play through new game modes, score systems and more!
--
New Songs Include:
- Paranoia (Remix)
- Violence (Part 1)
- Tomb (Remix)

Listen to more by Nightmare Lyre: https://nightmarelyre.bandcamp.com/
--
Visit Our Website - https://lavoiestudios.ca/games/fret-smasher/

Join our Discord - https://discordapp.com/invite/F8vZW85

Follow our Twitter - https://twitter.com/FretSmasher
--
Developed and Published by: Lavoie Studios
